title: Southwest says explosion will hurt bookings
text:
Southwest says explosion will hurt bookings 1:48am IST - 01:15
Southwest Airlines warned that fallout from a fatal mid-air explosion last week will weigh on second-quarter bookings. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
